00259Dr 2               ; fcall_vmask = current record's first_field, fcall_lsize = its count.
00259Dr 2               ; Each iteration consumes ".name" and walks one level deeper.  When the
00259Dr 2               ; resolved field is itself a RECORD and another '.' follows, repeat;
00259Dr 2               ; otherwise emit LDIND on the final scalar address.
00259Dr 2  A5 rr                LDA     tok_type
00259Fr 2  C9 22                CMP     #TOK_DOT
0025A1r 2  F0 0D                BEQ     @rrf_chain
